right \\u00a9 2024 NPR.\", \"from\": 22692, \"to\": 22753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22749, \"end\": 22752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999960181359862, \"rank\": 3.861914922589643e-06, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 22755, \"to\": 22775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Visit our websiteterms of useandpermissionspages atwww.npr.orgfor further information.Accuracy and availability of NPR transcripts may vary.\", \"from\": 22777, \"to\": 22917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22892, \"end\": 22895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999960181359862, \"rank\": 3.861914922589643e-06, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Transcript text may be revised to correct errors or match updates to audio.\", \"from\": 22918, \"to\": 22993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Audio on npr.org may be edited after its original broadcast or publication.\", \"from\": 22994, \"to\": 23069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The authoritative record of NPR's programming is the audio record.\", \"from\": 23070, \"to\": 23136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23098, \"end\": 23101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.999999998236035, \"rank\": 1.750331096410264e-09, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BRIAN MANN, BYLINE: Hi Juana.\", \"from\": 23138, \"to\": 23167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23138, \"end\": 23148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\", \"score\": 0.9999999900570629, \"rank\": 9.94251238918079e-09, \"text\": \"BRIAN MANN\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wow.\", \"from\": 23168, \"to\": 23172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a night.SUMMERS: It has been quite a night, indeed.\", \"from\": 23173, \"to\": 23229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, Brian, there is been so much anticipation around this race for Noah Lyles, the 100-meter champion.\", \"from\": 23230, \"to\": 23336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23301, \"end\": 23311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was going for the double in the 200-meter final.\", \"from\": 23337, \"to\": 23388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We saw him bound out when he was introduced.\", \"from\": 23389, \"to\": 23433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was full of that characteristic energy, that showmanship that he is known for, hoping to be the 10th man ever to win both of those races in a single summer games.\", \"from\": 23434, \"to\": 23599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, why do not you pick it up from here?\", \"from\": 23600, \"to\": 23643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Walk us through what happened.MANN: Yeah, it was clear, Juana, right from the start, that something was different with Noah Lyles.\", \"from\": 23644, \"to\": 23774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23763, \"end\": 23773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had that dominant showing Sunday in the 100-meter race.\", \"from\": 23775, \"to\": 23833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But today, he trailed behind Letsile Tebogo of Botswana and Kenny Bednarek of the U.S. - never seriously challenged them for the lead.\", \"from\": 23834, \"to\": 23968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23881, \"end\": 23889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9431204621385137, \"rank\": 0.06029924207087962, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 23894, \"end\": 23908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That powerful late kick that he's famous for never came.\", \"from\": 23969, \"to\": 24025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, at the finish line, he collapsed.\", \"from\": 24026, \"to\": 24065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He stayed on the ground, then rose to one knee, had to call for help.\", \"from\": 24066, \"to\": 24135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was later helped off the field.SUMMERS: Yeah, he seemed to be having a really tough time at the end there, and it's not like what we are used to seeing from him, Brian.\", \"from\": 24136, \"to\": 24307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What can you tell us about what happened?MANN: Yeah, so Noah Lyles has now confirmed in an interview with NBC that he competed after being diagnosed with COVID.\", \"from\": 24308, \"to\": 24468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24364, \"end\": 24374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 24414, \"end\": 24417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9752341173911545, \"rank\": 0.022207274758592913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, two days ago, he woke up feeling terrible, and he was tested.\", \"from\": 24469, \"to\": 24539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We also have a statement from U.S. Track and Field, saying they were aware of this test.\", \"from\": 24540, \"to\": 24628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They knew that he was running sick today.\", \"from\": 24629, \"to\": 24670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They say that was his choice.\", \"from\": 24671, \"to\": 24700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. Track and Field says they did follow all the necessary safety and health protocols.\", \"from\": 24701, \"to\": 24789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Noah Lyles was around a lot of these other athletes, so there are going to be some big questions asked about this decision to have him included in this race.\", \"from\": 24790, \"to\": 24951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24794, \"end\": 24804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember, Juana, Noah Lyles has suffered from asthma and allergies in the past.\", \"from\": 24952, \"to\": 25031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24969, \"end\": 24979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's talked about that.\", \"from\": 25032, \"to\": 25055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite all this, he still managed to win bronze.SUMMERS: That's right.\", \"from\": 25056, \"to\": 25127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure we are going to be hearing a lot more about this story.\", \"from\": 25128, \"to\": 25193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, I do want to ask you to put his performance into context - what he was attempting to do.\", \"from\": 25194, \"to\": 25289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just how difficult would it have been and how rare would it have been for Lyles to pull off wins in both the 100-meter, as he did earlier in the week, and the 200-meter, which he attempted to do today?MANN: Yeah, winning these two races in one Olympics is so rare.\", \"from\": 25290, \"to\": 25554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25364, \"end\": 25369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.5665125515503097, \"rank\": 0.7329260174760622, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only nine men have done it before.\", \"from\": 25555, \"to\": 25589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of those men, Jamaican Usain Bolt, did it at three straight Olympics.\", \"from\": 25590, \"to\": 25663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25608, \"end\": 25616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9937051038437701, \"rank\": 0.00633146901597152, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time an American pulled this off was Carl Lewis 40 years ago, in 1984.\", \"from\": 25664, \"to\": 25743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25681, \"end\": 25689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9994380751338291, \"rank\": 0.00042052759097618457, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 25710, \"end\": 25720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lewis was actually here in the stadium tonight watching.\", \"from\": 25744, \"to\": 25800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But again, along with the rest of us, he saw something very different happen - Noah Lyles coming in with a bronze-medal finish.SUMMERS: Brian, while I have you, I do want to ask you about something else that happened here tonight.\", \"from\": 25801, \"to\": 26031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minutes after the 200-meter men's race, Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone won the women's 400-meter hurdle race in dominant fashion.\", \"from\": 26032, \"to\": 26156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26072, \"end\": 26078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9925667901216783, \"rank\": 0.007040451843157832, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was incredible to watch.\", \"from\": 26157, \"to\": 26184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tell us what happened.MANN: Yeah, American Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone has been remarkable this year.\", \"from\": 26185, \"to\": 26284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26219, \"end\": 26227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995543430871968, \"rank\": 0.0003875082801241339, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 26228, \"end\": 26234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9925667901216783, \"rank\": 0.007040451843157832, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In national trials just a few weeks ago, she set the world record in the 400-meter hurdles.\", \"from\": 26285, \"to\": 26376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Juana, she actually runs the 400-meter hurdles faster than many professional athletes run 400 meters even without hurdles in their way.\", \"from\": 26377, \"to\": 26512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was dominant again, once again broke the world record and took gold for the United States.\", \"from\": 26513, \"to\": 26607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26593, \"end\": 26606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9337636330402237, \"rank\": 0.056698176690902546, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A very powerful week - despite the setback for Noah Lyles, we have seen just some incredible performances from American athletes on the track so far.SUMMERS: That's NPRs Brian Mann.\", \"from\": 26608, \"to\": 26789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26655, \"end\": 26665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 26719, \"end\": 26727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995543430871968, \"rank\": 0.0003875082801241339, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 26778, \"end\": 26788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\", \"score\": 0.9999999900570629, \"rank\": 9.94251238918079e-09, \"text\": \"Brian Mann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are both part of the NPR team that has been here covering the Paris Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 26790, \"to\": 26877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26814, \"end\": 26817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999960181359862, \"rank\": 3.861914922589643e-06, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, thank you.MANN: Thank you, Juana.Copyright \\u00a9 2024 NPR.\", \"from\": 26878, \"to\": 26939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26935, \"end\": 26938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999960181359862, \"rank\": 3.861914922589643e-06, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 26941, \"to\": 26961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Visit our websiteterms of useandpermissionspages atwww.npr.orgfor further information.Accuracy and availability of NPR transcripts may vary.\", \"from\": 26963, \"to\": 27103