earing a lot more about this story.\", \"from\": 55181, \"to\": 55246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, I do want to ask you to put his performance into context - what he was attempting to do.\", \"from\": 55247, \"to\": 55342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just how difficult would it have been and how rare would it have been for Lyles to pull off wins in both the 100-meter, as he did earlier in the week, and the 200-meter, which he attempted to do today?MANN: Yeah, winning these two races in one Olympics is so rare.\", \"from\": 55343, \"to\": 55607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55417, \"end\": 55422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7336950964412635, \"rank\": 0.31894872238168803, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only nine men have done it before.\", \"from\": 55608, \"to\": 55642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of those men, Jamaican Usain Bolt, did it at three straight Olympics.\", \"from\": 55643, \"to\": 55716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55661, \"end\": 55669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9995262990346285, \"rank\": 0.00047388715892194015, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time an American pulled this off was Carl Lewis 40 years ago, in 1984.\", \"from\": 55717, \"to\": 55796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55734, \"end\": 55742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993329854385699, \"rank\": 0.0005726027589065963, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 